quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,20,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza, mugondere Katonda n’omubakawe, temumuvangako, ate nga muwulira (bya bagamba)"
  8,21,Temubeera nga abo ab’agamba nti tuwulidde so nga tebawulira
  8,22,"Mazima e kiramu e kisinga obubi ewa Katonda, be ba kiggala, ba kasiru abo abatategeera"
  8,23,"Singa Katonda yabamanyaamu akalungi konna, yaalibawulizza, ate ne bwe yaalibawulizza, baaliwuguse nebava ku mazima"
  8,24,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza, mwanukule Katonda n’omubaka bwabayita okujja eri ekyo ekibawa obulamu, era mumanye nti, mazima Katonda, assa ekyawula wakati w’omuntu n’omutimagwe, so ng’ate bulijjo, mazima gyali gye mugenda okukunganyizibwa"
  8,25,"Mutye e kikemo e kitagenda kukwata ku abo abeeyisa obubi mu mmwe bokka, era mumanye nti mazima Katonda muyitirivu wa kubonereza"
  8,26,"Mujjukire we mwali abatono, nga muyisibwa bubi mu nsi, nga mutya abantu okubagajambula, n'abawa obubudamu, n’abawagira n’okutaasakwe, n’abagabirira mu birungi, olwo nno mube nga mwebaza"
  8,27,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza, temukumpanyanga Katonda n’omubaka, nemukumpanya obuvunaanyizibwa bwa mmwe, ng’ate ddala mumanyi"
  8,28,"Era mumanye nti mazima e mmaali ya mmwe, n’abaana ba mmwe kikemo, era nga bulijjo mazima ddala Katonda, alina empeera ensukkulumu"